{{Otheruses|Victory}}
'''Victory Square''' was an open plaza on [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]] that was constructed after the [[Yuuzhan Vong War]] as a memorial to all beings, including [[Yuuzhan Vong]], that aided in ending the conflict.

